ko 2 ( english : ko 2 ) is a 2016 indian tamil political thriller film written and directed by sarath . the film features bobby simha , nikki galrani , prakash raj and nikki galrani in the leading roles , while prakash raj and rj balaji play supporting roles . the film , produced by r. &lt;unk&gt; , had musical score by deva and was released on 14 june 2016 .